Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.41,0:10:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智花！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴哥哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年轻真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  阿昴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  真是谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有智花待在家里的话  果然还是很可怜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且如果阿昴带着一起去的话  我也会很放心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到家里会同意我出来  稍稍吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.68,0:11:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还见到昴哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件浴衣和你很配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会来得太早了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合的地点在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.24,0:11:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖水果糖的摊位前面  电话好像接不通
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  很快就能汇合的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还有时间  先去逛一下小摊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罚球的摊位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得来到这里  要试一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着浴衣的话  不知道能不能投准呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我给奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智花只要三投两中的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.27,0:11:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就什么都答应你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.98,0:12:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不管是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了！三球都完美入框
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害啊  智花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了昴哥哥为我加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:28.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  昴哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就  就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.06,0:12:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才说好的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事啊  奖励是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.44,0:12:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请和我一起看烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这次祭典结束时放的那个烟火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.00,0:12:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能地靠近一点
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在昴哥哥的身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.71,0:13:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  在我身边一起看吧  烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.55,0:13:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔舔~舔舔~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小智发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~智花已经到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.19,0:13:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  和长谷川哥哥一起刚从罚球摊位出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  那么快去和她们汇合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.91,0:13:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦  难得的二人世界
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就先去做自己喜欢的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.70,0:13:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~  日向也想去捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后想去吃巧克力香蕉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.96,0:13:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么这里就兵分两路之后再汇合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.80,0:13:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃棉花糖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  集合的地方是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家还没到么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智花？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.78,0:14:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说  想上厕所？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.00,0:14:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  一直忍着  然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.42,0:14:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走不了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.05,0:14:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.55,0:14:26.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.97,0:14:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能赶上真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.48,0:14:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别挡路啊  大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.70,0:14:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是眼镜掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.74,0:14:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:59.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  这里有人掉了眼镜  请帮忙找一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.30,0:15:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这副吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  谢谢你热心帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  能够找到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.14,0:15:19.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来找我家女儿的  但是对人群没辙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能体会  我也是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:25.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.66,0:15:34.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会让我分神的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这不是夏阳嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做啥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好好玩的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.80,0:15:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊  笨蛋真帆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.55,0:15:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帆就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿  柊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  随便你怎么玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我觉得你肯定不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:17.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥  等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,椿和柊  还是一样的不饶人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样你会摔下去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.34,0:16:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真帆  纱季
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  射击啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内裤要露出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿昴  不准看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊  阿昴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:17:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帆  都怪你冲太前面才会被人看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么纱季也试试啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看不到内裤我就原谅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能会看得到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样  用腋下夹住试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.89,0:17:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是谢谢你教我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舔舔~舔舔~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦~好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好棒的视野
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.46,0:17:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是个意外不错的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多该放烟火了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.59,0:17:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智花
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该说过不准你外出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.36,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是担任慧心学园女篮部教练的长谷川昴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自把智花带出来  真的非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有…不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我拜托妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:35.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  到头来就是我打破了约定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:37.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.47,0:18:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但智花不是什么坏孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懂礼貌  对打篮球也很认真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  说得好像你什么都知道似的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得她来这里也不是把和父亲的约定抛诸脑后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是单纯地想和同伴们在一起而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.95,0:19:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对她来说  这就是如此重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说是同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:09.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智花不需要打篮球的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你是刚才的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是智花的教练？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.35,0:19:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是这些孩子们的教练
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们需要小智
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊  如果不是阿智
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会知道打篮球是这么帅气又愉快的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日向也喜欢智花  最喜欢和大家在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为智花  多亏有智花在我们才能打篮球
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外出的事我道歉  但是请不要说大家的坏话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全靠大家和昴哥哥  我才能再一次享受篮球的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.30,0:20:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要从大家身边抢走智花  也不要赶走智花身边的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求您了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.82,0:20:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了  随你喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.66,0:20:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,智花曾经因为篮球而有过悲伤的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  似乎这次通过篮球而遇到了很好的同伴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是个冒昧的请求  我女儿今后也麻烦你指教了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.81,0:20:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.36,0:21:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  履行刚才的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.76,0:21:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉今天发挥的特别好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么好事发生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.10,0:21:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸对我说了「篮球也好好加油吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs17\pos(320,325)}真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.03,0:21:46.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Très  Bien
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.58,0:21:52.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:01.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.92,0:22:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.85,0:23:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.10,0:23:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真帆  冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}哇哦～～～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.10,0:23:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的预告时间也很紧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:40.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}汪！汪！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.68,0:23:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是  我和昴哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}喵～！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.52,0:23:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在早上练习的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:43.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}噢噢～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！小智  务必注意不要剧透哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}啊哇哇哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.44,0:23:46.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先打个招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.82,0:23:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.48,0:23:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回也请准时收看！
